Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.67,0:00:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is Burnett, ARUS Golden News.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.88,0:00:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did you all witness that shocking video
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:15.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,message from the Dorssian chancellor?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.60,0:00:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We have come here to Module 77's hangar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.89,0:00:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing at the Phantom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.64,0:00:23.98,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What could be the truth \Nbehind those images?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.40,0:00:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To be honest, this may be the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.83,0:00:28.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I have ever sensed anything this eerie.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.11,0:00:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this? It's full of people!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.62,0:00:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is being done to these people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.22,0:00:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.68,0:00:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.31,0:01:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Iori...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.56,0:01:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.65,0:01:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No! Dad! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.57,0:01:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's no use, he's gone. \NWhat are they doing here?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.78,0:01:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a JIORan ship, \Nisn't it? Answer me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.58,0:01:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, make them stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.62,0:01:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Murderers!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.37,0:01:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.66,0:01:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? \NThat ship isn't ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.08,0:01:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Eileen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.51,0:01:30.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eileen!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.63,0:01:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Eileen!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.34,0:01:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why did this have to happen to her...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.05,0:01:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the truth behind Module 77!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.77,0:01:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Upon learning of the threat they posed,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.86,0:01:47.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,we made the difficult \Ndecision to invade JIOR.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.02,0:01:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the good of the entire world, \Nwe took a stand against them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They fought against us \Nwith unkillable soldiers!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.99,0:01:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Before you censure Dorssia,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:58.29,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to see the \Nreality for yourselves.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will say this again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The creatures that dwell within \NModule 77 are not human beings!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.95,0:02:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They are monsters who survive by \Ndraining the life out of humans!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.97,0:03:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of house of horrors \Nhave we stumbled into?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've been lured into a monster's nest?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prime Minister Sashinami, \NI demand an explanation!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.81,0:03:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,0:03:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were going to tell you about \Nthe Phantom after the summit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto? What is that? \NWhat's this "Phantom"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You knew? You knew about \Nthat strange ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This was a close brush with death.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If the Dorssian chancellor's accusation \Nhad come just a little later,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we would have ended up on \Nthese monsters' dinner plates!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In accordance with international law,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hereby designate the \Nresidents of Module 77
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as Class 7 Special Hazard Organisms!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This was inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got too close to the secrets \Nlurking in the shadows of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.16,0:04:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, it played out exactly \Naccording to your plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.19,0:04:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have known.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is nothing that warrants \Nbeing praised over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On the contrary,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.88,0:04:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm rather disappointed that the \Nresistance I expected failed to materialize.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do they mean, monsters?! \NWe're human beings!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be some kind of mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What have you been \Ngoing on and on about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you what you \Nguys did down on Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it just the pilots \Nwho are those monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.77,0:05:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, dial it down! We \Ndidn't do anything—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.13,0:05:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're another one like \NRukino, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fess up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you people doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are the strange ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you really go \Ndown to Earth to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's right! That weird ship \Nbelongs to you guys, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone who went \Ndown to Earth a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Everyone, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We all risked our lives to go to Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.05,0:05:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Mr. President, hear \Nour side of the story!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yohei?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be some mistake! \NPlease, Mr. President—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.97,0:05:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's been shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yohei! Yohei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't human!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're Class 7 Special \NHazard Organisms!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're creatures who have survived \Nall this time by fooling us humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't waste your compassion on them! \NThink of it as vermin eradication!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, we aren't—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.46,0:06:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, no more shooting! \NNo more killing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over my dead body!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.18,0:06:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Valvrave!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep this up, I shoot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. President, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the hangar \Nwas under our control!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.99,0:06:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't... Please don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let go! The students! The \Nstudents are being butchered!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you run out there without a plan, \Nyou'll just get yourself killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.26,0:07:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Moon! It's \Nneutral territory!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That rule only applies to human beings!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.65,0:07:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As far as they're concerned, \Nwe no longer count.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Attention, humans of Earth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am the president of ARUS.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Today, we have come face to face \Nwith a threat to humanity itself!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To meet this unprecedented \Ndanger, we have made a decision.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The decision to set aside \Nlong-standing grudges
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:31.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and come together as \Na single human race!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Today, we announce the formation \Nof the ARUS/Dorssia Allied Forces!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our countries will immediately assemble \Nall our forces on the Moon's surface!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As a joint force, we will launch a \Nconcerted attack against Module 77,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:48.32,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,the threat against humanity!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a battle which we must not lose!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the future of all humanity!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Valvrave pilots, can you hear me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Allied Forces are going to \Nswarm all over us soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:23.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,This Module is a lost cause.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want you to rescue as many \Nstudents as possible and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:28.27,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,guide them to the hangar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll escape in shuttles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otamaya! Take your buddies \Nand get to the hangar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about Units 1 and 5?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.72,0:08:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep 'em safe! Just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.22,0:08:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to bring the weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Keep moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We have three shuttles! \NSplit up and get aboard!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot, she's already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, she's coming with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.74,0:08:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think she's gonna \Ncome back to life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:08:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? \NBecause she's my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but we can't bring her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In a situation like this, \Nwe can't save everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But we've been friends \Nsince middle school!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stay calm, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look at everything \Nwe've survived so far!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're going to be \Nfine this time, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have faith in the classmates around \Nyou and let's make it through this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.31,0:09:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You had a reason for \Nthis, right, Haruto?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This can't... This can't be happening!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.03,0:09:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Save the regrets for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:38.14,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone else die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's get moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:41.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The space shuttles are \Nalready launching!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're all right now. We are, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm picking up ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.43,0:09:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This number can't be right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Put it on the monitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Answer my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You had possessed \NK-zwölf's body, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.16,0:10:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In which case, you had ample \Nopportunity to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't intend to answer me, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, let's return \Nto the more pressing topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The matter of L-elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our only option is a high-velocity \Nlaunch using the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.29,0:10:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,mass driver to blast \Nthrough the combat zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Valvraves, protect the \Nmass driver and ships until
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.27,0:10:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all three shuttles successfully launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're going on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you rendezvous with \Nthe last shuttle, Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As soon as they're ready, \Nmeet up with them right away!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.73,0:11:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you get left behind, it's all over!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One shuttle left!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.98,0:12:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mass driver damaged! Energy \Nsupply system down 40%!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.06,0:12:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Necessary charging time for \Nlaunching now 720 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.73,0:12:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible! We can't \Npossibly hold out that long!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.62,0:12:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Receiving external transmission!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's... The president of ARUS!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ARUS?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My memories are disappearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.96,0:12:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.85,0:12:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We have a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:56.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,There are Dorssian soldiers \Naboard the shuttle!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:12:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It looks like they snuck \Naboard during the escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:01.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and they're holding everyone hostage!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood! I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone okay? Where's \Nthe Dorssian soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto, don't! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Run from what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.19,0:13:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.40,0:13:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Iori, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.61,0:13:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The president of ARUS gave us his word.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.48,0:13:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we handed over the Valvrave pilots,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he would spare the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you blame us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, the rest of \Nus are human beings!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.16,0:13:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones who eat humans \Nare you and the other monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Iori! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto! Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Come on! You can't be dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.81,0:14:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you shoot him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto's... He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-He killed my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They killed him! Haruto \Nkilled him and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was shot. Right through the heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's alive. He really is one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did I tell you? He's a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're one too, Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shoko, hear me out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You knew everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,About Miss Rukino?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About that ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me about your body?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.36,0:15:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believed in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was because you were there \Nthat I was able to hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how bad a scrape I was in,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always had faith that \Nyou were the one person
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:15:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who would always be by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:16:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just like in the cave when \Nwe ran away from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ran way? The cave?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? We ran away? When was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My head hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there was \Nsomething more here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm positive that there \Nwas something. But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:27.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,there's nothing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.49,0:16:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What did I lose?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Haruto that I knew is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.54,0:16:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking \Nabout, Shoko? I'm—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.87,0:16:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me, you liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been lying to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prime Minister, your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All Valvraves, please stand down!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shoko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are going to hand \Nover Haruto Tokishima
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.03,0:17:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and surrender to the Allied Forces.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.16,0:17:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.12,0:17:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shoko, what are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the only way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have an obligation to \Nprotect everyone's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.76,0:17:30.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As prime minister.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think we've been \Nfighting all this time for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make yourselves out to be heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're nothing but monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All this time, you've been killing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,people while you were \Npretending to be our friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just like you killed my father!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.69,0:17:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Monsters, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's got nothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.77,0:17:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no telling what he might do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous to take him with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You give me too much credit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.76,0:18:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's it doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.06,0:18:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No! This isn't what he said!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.15,0:18:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.36,0:18:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they honestly think \Nthat the president
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of a country would \Nnegotiate with vermin?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He lied to us? No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's run! Fire the mass driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't! It's not charged yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why? You're a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're not monsters!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.06,0:19:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're Kamitsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aina came up with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said we were touched by God, \Nso she called us "kamitsuki."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If he's everyone's God,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.99,0:19:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but is so stingy that \Nhe only saves those
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who believe in him, forget him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.29,0:19:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you don't believe us,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.96,0:19:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if you hate us, I'm \Nstill gonna save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stay back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.37,0:19:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You and Akira, stick \Nclose to the shuttle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.59,0:19:31.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Escape with them using the mass driver!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What about you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.34,0:19:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll rescue Haruto!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.76,0:19:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inuzuka-senpai, what are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.38,0:19:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been watching you \Nand Haruto for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna end like \Nthis? I don't buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.42,0:19:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.31,0:19:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Charging complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.68,0:19:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada, I'll let you block \Nthe shot! Use my shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.16,0:19:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.74,0:20:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now to... get Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.29,0:20:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shoko and the others are in the clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:54.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The last order of business is you two.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:21:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll at least... get \Nyou to the Module...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.56,0:21:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's no use! Leave us \Nand escape by yourself!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.06,0:21:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.86,0:21:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel about Shoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.54,0:21:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How can you ask me that \Nat a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.59,0:21:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It occurred to me that I'd \Nnever heard it straight
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.54,0:21:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the horse's mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.92,0:21:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.91,0:21:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I liked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.21,0:21:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I still like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.89,0:21:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I bet I always will.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.65,0:22:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. I knew it all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.08,0:22:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.74,0:24:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, episode 22. \N"Fist of the Moon."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.22,0:24:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Valvrave the Liberator...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.23,0:24:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.23,0:24:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The system that will expose \Nthe truth of the world.